queries.query:
from(bucket: "windtunnel")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "wt.instruments.operation_duration")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["operation_id"] == "admin_install_app")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["scenario_name"] == "app_install")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["run_id"] == v.RunId)  
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "value")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["is_error"] == "false")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> yield(name: "mean")

from(bucket: "windtunnel")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "wt.custom.app_install")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "value")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["scenario_name"] == "app_install")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["happ"] == "callback")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["run_id"] == v.RunId)
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({ r with _value: r._value * 1000.0 }))  
  |> yield(name: "mean")
